Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.51,0:00:23.77,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我没有做错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:36.28,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:39.85,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,又做噩梦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.22,0:00:43.10,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.51,0:00:46.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我的家里有一台机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.77,0:00:50.86,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,租约已经续了七年了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:52.71,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你今天几点回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.78,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我可能会晚一点回
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:00:56.63,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,抱歉  乔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.49,0:01:03.87,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,他比任何男人都要真诚  善良
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,满足了我身心的需求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.29,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,与之相比…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.47,0:01:11.30,Default,Man,0,0,0,,久等了  静香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:14.80,Default,Man,0,0,0,,抱歉  我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.01,0:01:20.05,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,人类男性真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:31.65,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:35.13,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,欢迎回家  静香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:36.40,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,晚饭准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.40,0:01:37.58,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.12,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我有工作没能做完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.68,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,实在没法在下班前做完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.68,0:01:49.29,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,就只能留下来加了会儿班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.07,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,然后我就在车站晃悠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.58,0:02:02.92,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,已经七年了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.08,0:02:07.42,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,无论是高兴还是沮丧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:10.17,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,我见证了你各种各样的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:14.32,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,但是  我觉得你可能是时候迎接新的人生了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.43,0:02:16.28,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你觉得呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.65,0:02:26.14,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,不要哭  静香
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:28.96,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,抱歉  乔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.36,0:02:30.08,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.62,0:02:33.26,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.18,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,这是件好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.92,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你不需要道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:41.61,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你不生气吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.61,0:02:42.54,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.54,0:02:44.09,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.68,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,你无法生气吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:51.21,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,因为你只是制造出来讨女孩子欢心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.21,0:02:53.24,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,男朋友机器人罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:59.94,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.62,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,「产业 AI」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:10.96,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那是制造出来辅助人类生活的人工智能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.72,0:03:15.64,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,能力有限的产业 AI  不会产生「心」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.51,0:03:19.20,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,人类以此来区分它们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.20,0:03:20.85,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,并将它们作为商品来使用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:22.41,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:58.65,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:01.23,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我是须堂新医学诊所的须堂医生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:02.59,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我叫波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:04.26,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你好啊  波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.31,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你好  须堂医生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.31,0:05:09.89,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我们什么时候变成修玩具的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.47,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,看来是治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.85,0:05:16.85,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:19.00,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.27,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.26,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他的记忆储存坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.94,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,毕竟已经是非常老旧的了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:27.40,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我已经治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.29,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,太好了  波波
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.18,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,修好了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:36.52,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,其实不修也挺好的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.73,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.73,0:05:40.03,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,你也是男子汉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.27,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,不要再依靠那种东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.27,0:05:44.87,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你这种说法  波波会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.87,0:05:46.36,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,波波会伤心的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.86,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,不会的  它只是机器
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.10,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,才不是呢  他是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.10,0:05:54.51,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  妈妈  不要吵架  不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.92,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,波波不要插嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:56.88,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.09,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我是不是好心办了坏事…？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.09,0:06:02.50,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.73,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.69,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我开动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:14.20,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,这种日常  又要继续了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.20,0:06:15.52,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,好啦  好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.77,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,再说了  波波不是你买来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.42,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,那是我再婚之前的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.82,0:06:35.18,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:37.66,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,妈妈  小熊动了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:39.84,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,真是太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:41.99,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:42.97,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,健次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.43,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我叫波波
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.21,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你好  波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:48.85,Default,Poppo,0,800,0,,你好  小健
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:50.46,Default,Mariko,0,800,0,,{\fad(0,250)}是我错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:02.51,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,我本希望它能多少消除些单亲家庭的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:05.05,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,送给他的时候没有想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.61,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,他肯定会高兴的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:12.87,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,没有妈妈也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:15.25,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我有你了啊  波波
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.25,0:07:18.54,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我会永远和你在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:19.75,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,约好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:23.78,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我不会因为工作而抛下你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.37,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,就算妈妈不在  我也会陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.86,0:07:35.18,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,那只小熊一下就成为孩子重要的家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:39.31,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,健次已经不是小孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.49,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,到时候就会意识到  波波只是个玩具的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:43.73,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,这可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.28,0:07:46.48,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,明明只是按照程序运作而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:48.78,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,但它叽叽喳喳说个不停  真是让人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.27,0:07:55.62,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,好不容易才治好了你  妈妈却摆个臭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.73,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,但是  不要和妈妈吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.84,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,Flashback,不要再依靠那种东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.84,0:08:06.55,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我就必须要丢下你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:10.51,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,明明你都约好要永远在一起了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.34,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,永远在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:21.06,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,谁在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.02,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,和我一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:25.09,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,怎么了  波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.82,0:08:32.30,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:33.36,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.24,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.61,0:08:38.75,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:45.50,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,又坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:52.84,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,从那天起就怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:55.23,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,他老问我陌生人的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.89,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我不奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:09:01.06,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,那你告诉我  小雪是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.42,0:09:05.44,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,这不能告诉陌生人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:08.44,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,我不是陌生人吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:11.11,Default,Kenji,0,1300,0,,到底怎么回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.74,0:09:12.69,Default,Risa,500,0,0,,是病毒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:13.41,Default,Kenji,0,1300,0,,波波  波波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.61,Default,Sudo,500,0,0,,不  恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.61,Default,Mariko,0,1300,0,,健次！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.49,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:22.62,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,你竟敢偷拿我的钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.70,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,因  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.70,0:09:27.33,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,放任波波这样也太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:28.75,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,你差不多得了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.38,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,那台机器人不是活着的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.38,0:09:32.87,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,只是做得很好的玩具而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.87,0:09:33.80,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,不要这么说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:36.22,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  妈妈  不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.93,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,不要吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.56,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,那台机器的喜怒哀乐全都是虚假的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:44.97,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,只是给出看似合理的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:47.05,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,它是没有自我意识和感情的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.47,0:09:53.70,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,不是的  才不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:56.07,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:59.55,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,虽然不知能否恢复原样  但先让我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.45,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不收钱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.84,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这样就没问题了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:14.09,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,内部数据解析完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.46,0:10:16.72,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,帮我生成个可视化报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:17.95,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:24.60,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:34.07,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,医生  你很了解机器人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.84,0:10:35.86,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.29,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波他有「心」吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:39.29,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,都说了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.33,0:10:45.87,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,随着科学进步  人脑的秘密也被揭晓了大半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:49.51,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但是对于「心」定义  人们众说纷纭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.39,0:10:54.65,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,说不定所谓的「心」  根本就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.53,0:11:00.26,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,言归正传  我知道小雪是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.71,0:11:04.75,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我查看了记忆数据后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:07.19,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,发现了二十年前的数据
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.89,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这只小熊应该是买的二手之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.60,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,诶？ 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.92,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那么  小雪应该就是这只小熊之前的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.85,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,换句话说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:22.01,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,这种问题在过去的计算机里很常见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.01,0:11:24.88,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,就算表面看上去记忆已经删除了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.60,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,但数据本身还留存在储存系统内
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.31,0:11:31.22,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,上次我在抢救数据的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.22,0:11:35.10,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,把他以前的记忆连同新的记忆一起恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.80,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,如果把旧的数据删除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:40.76,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,那小熊基本上可以恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:42.27,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,你想怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.21,0:11:51.02,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,所以  他怎么选？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.41,0:11:56.71,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,健次吵着说「要是删除小雪的回忆  那波波会伤心的」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.71,0:11:59.32,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,最后就直接这么带回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:06.85,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,那孩子这么依赖波波  是因为你和我再婚的缘故吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:11.53,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,总之  得想办法把他们俩分开才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.71,0:12:17.71,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,明天趁他上学时  我去叫回收人员来带走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.45,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪  你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.41,0:12:38.70,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.61,0:12:42.55,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,今天过得非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:48.03,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我留下最后的回忆  静香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.79,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.39,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,嗯  很有纪念意义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.82,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但你很快就会忘记了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:17.19,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,我们该告别了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.69,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,再见了  乔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.66,0:13:25.45,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,感谢您选用本公司的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:31.46,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你与租赁机器人乔的租约今日结束
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.97,0:13:36.46,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,与你生活的数据会在总部服务器中保存五年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:39.41,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,如果你和男友之间进展不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.41,0:13:41.24,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,请使用「复活」咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:46.22,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,五年后又怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:51.97,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,一切的回忆都终会消逝的  静香
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.44,0:13:58.35,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,离家出走？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.86,0:14:01.11,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,没有  他没来我们这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.54,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,你联系警察了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:09.50,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,健次…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.14,0:14:15.01,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.50,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你找我有什么事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.53,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.65,0:14:26.01,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你不伤心吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.86,0:14:37.14,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,我一切的行为举止都是预先编制好的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,学校里有教过…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.87,0:14:44.15,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,在过去人们也曾认为仿生人是机器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:45.98,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,但是现在不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.49,0:14:47.44,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:51.99,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,我们机器人是制造出来服务人类的商品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.99,0:14:54.81,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,机器人和仿生人不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.81,0:14:56.88,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,千万不可以忘记这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.88,0:15:00.62,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,但是  刚才的姐姐都哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:04.13,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,不会有人在丢弃牙刷时流泪的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.68,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,所以  哥哥也有…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.68,0:15:10.69,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,机器人也拥有「心」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.69,0:15:12.39,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,一定是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.55,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.33,0:15:19.92,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,在她的眼中  我可能的确拥有「心」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.36,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.36,0:15:24.86,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我叫波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:26.61,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你好啊  波波
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:29.49,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,你的顾客真是个好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:32.35,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,嗯  小健非常温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.84,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我超喜欢他的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:51.05,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,依据保密协议
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.05,0:15:54.17,Default,Navi,0,0,0,,现在重置乔的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.81,0:16:09.03,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  我们回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.26,0:16:13.15,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,这是因为你在担心我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.07,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,还是因为程序要你这么说？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:25.92,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  小健
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:32.09,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  这样会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.56,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,有没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:40.37,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,有没有人  请留步
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.34,0:16:44.23,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,有没有人  帮助小健…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.86,0:16:47.00,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,有没有人… 有没有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.87,Default,Crowd,0,0,0,,怎么了？怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.62,Default,Man,0,0,0,,什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.62,0:17:04.25,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,不要吓我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:06.05,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,只是个玩具而已啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:06.85,Default,Woman,0,0,0,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:09.01,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.42,0:17:16.63,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,是我的错！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:20.10,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,是我没有看好他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.00,0:17:42.91,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,终于睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.33,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,是吗  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:50.64,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,不是挺好的嘛  健次也平安回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.64,0:17:52.04,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.59,0:17:56.86,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,会感冒的… 有没有人  请留步…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.84,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,有没有… 人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.85,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,真理子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.03,0:18:08.10,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,你认为是波波牺牲自己去拦车吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:11.62,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,我觉得你是想多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.52,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,你  你说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:15.11,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.77,0:18:17.15,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,当然是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.29,Default,Ryo,0,0,0,,把他带到医院去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.95,0:18:28.12,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,请交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:37.93,Default,Jay,0,0,0,,准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.64,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:44.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我们什么时候变成修玩具的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.18,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,手术开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:56.12,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:57.77,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.42,0:19:01.29,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,他肯定能得救的  没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.24,0:19:12.17,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪在这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.56,0:19:15.67,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,嗯  医生帮我们查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.68,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,波波  小雪就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:29.11,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你和小雪关系好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:30.10,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.94,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我们一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:34.94,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,但是突然有一天  就见不到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:41.45,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈都不肯告诉我小雪到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:46.70,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,但我想要再见到她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:49.95,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,因为我们约好要永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.98,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小雪  终于又见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:06.17,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:20.40,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,「机器人没有心」么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.41,0:20:23.19,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,你真的这么认为吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.41,0:20:27.69,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.74,Default,Mariko,0,0,0,,妈妈也不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:36.91,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,小健  这是海吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.91,0:20:38.21,Default,Kenji,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.05,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,我还是第一次看到海
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.69,Default,Poppo,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.87,0:20:55.98,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,发生什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.59,0:21:00.21,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,不知不觉  我脑子里净是在想乔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:04.86,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,说实话  这应该不需要什么治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.52,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,考虑过和现男友分手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.52,0:21:10.97,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,然后使用所谓的「复活」咒语吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.71,0:21:15.37,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是… 乔会怎么想呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:18.89,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,机器人是不会责怪你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.89,0:21:20.88,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,他们在制造时就是这样设定好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:24.63,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,但是我… 就这么轻易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:27.69,Default,Shizuka,0,0,0,,我要怎么面对乔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:38.68,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,须堂医生  你不是机器人有心派的人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.68,0:21:40.40,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我什么时候说过这句话？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:43.15,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,但  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.65,0:21:46.61,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,我只是想做只有我能做的治疗罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.61,0:21:47.91,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.41,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:54.12,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,须堂医生  要一起去吃饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.67,Default,Sudo,0,0,0,,又要我请客吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:21:58.92,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,我什么时候说过这句话？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:03.68,Default,Risa,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}不过  你要请客的话  我也不会拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.45,0:22:09.97,Default,Renter,0,0,0,,啊  来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:16.98,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,感谢您选用本公司的服务
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.72,Default,Joe,0,0,0,,我是租赁机器人  乔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.09,0:22:21.98,Default,Renter,0,0,0,,请  请多关照
